Description: RAAT for HiFiBerry
 RAAT is a Roon player for HiFiBerry devices, enabling multi-room audio
 playback and synchronization across devices. It is designed to work
 seamlessly with Roon's audio architecture, allowing users to enjoy
 high-quality audio streaming in multiple rooms or zones within their home
 network. RAAT supports various HiFiBerry hardware, including DACs and
 amplifiers, providing a flexible and powerful solution for audiophiles and
 music enthusiasts.
